snippet.title: The Super Mario Bros. Movie 64 DS Download + Playthrough
snippet.description:
Credit to the SM64DS Hacking Discord Server for offering help with various problems (especially pants64, who spent a long time teaching me stuff about this game.)
Join the SM64DS hacking Discord Server here: https://discord.gg/NYyFMe3

DOWNLOAD Revision 1: https://drive.google.com/file/d/1asJE9rWlN0Tmn7P4isfa-NE6LkXVwlz5/view?usp=sharing
Join my Discord server: https://discord.gg/GkPruBS
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/solarz

This project and all others are unpaid other than donations via Patreon, so consider donating above!

Comment your feedback and suggestions!

This romhack is compatible with real NDS hardware, DeSmuME, and presumably all other platforms capable of running NDS roms.

Music featured in this video:
Super Mario Bros. Theme - Nintendo
Majora's Mask 3D Final Hours - Nintendo
Mario & Luigi Raceway Mariokart Wii - Nintendo
